-- Drake & Scull Unit Wins $38 Million Contract For Abu Dhabi Worker Housing
-- Shaji Mathew
-- 2010-09-07T04:58:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/drake-scull-unit-wins-38-million-contract-for-abu-dhabi-worker-housing.html

          
          
             Drake & Scull International PJSC, an
engineering contractor for the real-estate industry, won a
contract valued at 140 million dirhams from Campco Properties
LLC in Abu Dhabi.  
 The contract won by Gulf Technical Construction Co. is for
the construction of labour accommodation, the company said in a
statement to the Dubai bourse today. Drake & Scull formed Campco
Properties earlier this year in partnership with Buhairan Ltd.  
          
          


  


        